[Auction "W"]
1NT 2S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 1, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "fe7b81da98486fe7d27eb90c625d34d94edab3999cdf5336ede48b558f6a68e7"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{You have a good 6-card suit but only 8 HCP. This is bare minimum for a DONT bid. The fact that your suit is \Ss should sway you toward bidding.

But with the weak hand you bid 2\S instead of double. Everybody passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "E:KQ7.AT653.AK3.J9 AJT.KJ7.QJ96.AT7 942.84.T82.K8542 8653.Q92.754.Q63"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "1NT"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
1NT pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: E, chBasis: E, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 1, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "a10c25a4e74cb98ccdeed39a1408d44f1b3e53f00a2032096018eea335013562"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{With 16 points and a balanced hand you were planning on opening 1NT yourself.

But one of the consequences of playing DONT is that you have no bid to describe this hand. You cannot double because then partner would just bid 2\C as a relay and you wouldn't know where to go.

So you pass.}

